{"tid":1829851,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］大家出晒去嘅時候，會有咩風向post？","createTime":"2020-01-19T06:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T09:08:19.000Z","uid":160257,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"834f3a115f45f4dd6b2e6cbfa42d8243f052cad9","tid":1829851,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"有勇武做嘢 = 最衰勇武搞到遊行結束<br />\n冇勇武做嘢 = 香港人淨係識叫口號<br />\n<br />\n有政黨擺街站 = 淨係識籌旗<br />\n冇政黨擺街站 = 乜嘢都唔做<br />\n<br />\n散場時有人殿後 = 又送頭被圍捕<br />\n散場時乜人都走晒 = 又開聯歡會<br />\n<br />\n更多情況不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">其實大家都知五毛嘅存在，佢地最叻扮演晒兩邊嘅人，帶風向引戰，通常說話內容冇乜建設性只會謾罵放負。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但同現實捉鬼一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會杜絕得晒</span>，何況討論區理應有不聲音，除時屌錯真心手足，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">只需要提高警覺，冷處理嗰啲post</span>，以免佢地上熱門，造成風向。<br />\n<br />\n同時盡可能推行動post或其他有用post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9101b22ac6b931c35d644b49a3b3fe62e4df45fd","tid":1829851,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00c688bc8a97b7f75edd7cf21a3f7f9954ae679b","tid":1829851,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dcf9c5b9794268d5de4403d18ab08402124cce","tid":1829851,"uid":277054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日英文口號一覽：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Liberate Hong Kong, <br />\nRevolution Now!</strong><br />\n<br />\nFive Demands, <br />\nNot One Less!<br />\n<br />\nFight For Freedom, <br />\nStand With Hong Kong!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Boycott China,<br />\nFight Together